OL,3,CEngland's driest start to spring in 69
OL,4,Cyears raises risk of summer drought
OL,6,FThe Environment Agency says it is
OL,7,Fmonitoring water company drought
OL,8,Fplans, supporting farmers with
OL,9,Firrigation advice, and preparing
OL,10,Fguidance for the public on how to save
OL,11,Fwater.
OL,13,FNational Farmers' Union vice president
OL,14,FRachel Hallos said the situation on
OL,15,Fthe ground remained variable across
OL,16,Ffarming sectors.
